      "span_text": "The finding that P. transvaalicus venom can be neutralized with a polyclonal antibody raised against the first 18 amino acid residues of birtoxin seems to be an exception [CITATION_1] though it remains to be seen if horse derived antivenom against A. crassicauda will neutralize the venom of P. transvaalicus."
